{
  "id": "RAW_f67cf591",
  "title": "Anthropic 和 OpenAI 同时开始撒钱倾销，AI 的“外卖大战”来了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247501561&idx=1&sn=8ef07c94a9a0728e49cc145a4e4efae3",
  "date": "2026-03-15 04:49:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ea15575&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fq6aOmBZKAbPDicncB8r9SrlqWibAdCLHPJCvQA0f6Tcg7XVto2scwhFQgwoEDGLc1L74x0l4qw3ETOtksqGnSWqFicbc5wGWJn1Mgibv7VLs38g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin: 0 auto;padding: 24px 20px 48px 20px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近一个月内，尤其是最近一周内，发生了一件挺有意思的事情：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 和 OpenAI 同时开始撒钱倾销了。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这让我想起来了去年国内上演的外卖大战 —— 也不知道最后谁买单了，反正当时用户全都薅到了，爽到了。</span></strong></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;font-weight: 700;margin: 32px 0px 14px;padding-left: 12px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(215, 26, 27);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;line-height: 1.35 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">发生了什么</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">三件事。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一件：Anthropic 100 万 token 上下文，不加钱了。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前，虽然Claude的Sonnet模型支持1M上下文窗口，但是你往模型里塞超过 20 万 token 的内容，要收 2-5 倍的溢价。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">在Claude Code 里，默认使用Opus 4.6模型，1M上下文窗口，不额外加钱。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">超长的工作流任务，Agent可以完成得更好了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外，我怀疑两年前流行过的RAG框架，正在迎来灭顶之灾。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6793154761904762\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2688\" style=\"display: block;width: 100%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;box-shadow: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22) 0px 16px 34px, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12) 0px 4px 10px;border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);margin: 30px auto !important;padding: 8px !important;border-radius: 14px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017905\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1a58774c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbOpicrKSmocYEJJ8YQ2bFTSO0kwsicbxXdcP2hPEjPIeQMLec9azJ4ZdbticZnq4NNk9hv4lWL0ky6gr5slWWtXENacIY2upGJgTs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二件：Anthropic 闲时用量翻倍。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 宣布，3月13日到27日，非高峰时段所有用户的用量直接翻倍。免费用户也有。全平台覆盖——网页版、桌面版、Claude Code、Cowork，全都算。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且——</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">额外用量不计入周限额。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">不是把你的额度提前花完，是纯粹额外送的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">高峰时间的意思是： 美东时间早上8点到下午2点，北京时间的晚上9点到凌晨3点。除此之外，全是薅羊毛时间。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">非常有趣——对于处于北京时间的我们来说，我们正常使用Claude Code的时间，全是人家的“闲时”！ （凌晨3点到第二天晚上21点，都是闲时，享受2倍额度；周末全天享受）</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们醒着的每一秒都在薅羊毛，睡觉的时候才是人家的高峰期。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个时区红利对我们来说简直是天上掉馅饼。也许还能顺便养成不要熬夜的好习惯，因为我们稍微一熬夜，就进入非羊毛时间了……</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7098214285714286\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2688\" style=\"display: block;width: 100%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;box-shadow: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22) 0px 16px 34px, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12) 0px 4px 10px;border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);margin: 30px auto !important;padding: 8px !important;border-radius: 14px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017907\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=23f99ca7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbPFoQWES1m1kHCgT2BwgrqVVlicoMq6ibIrwjSPsd61QQ3LRuEs1wMCicU4SicDroPCPz0fibwu6KicDibiaYo8HepH0rQrbhkJgEHku7E%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三件：OpenAI Codex 全线翻倍，送两个月。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI从2月就开始了，所有付费计划的 Codex 限额翻倍，一直送到 4月。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">效果如何？Codex 周活从不到 50 万暴涨到 160 万，一个月翻了三倍多。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6637931034482759\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1160\" style=\"display: block;width: 100%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;box-shadow: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22) 0px 16px 34px, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12) 0px 4px 10px;border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);margin: 30px auto !important;padding: 8px !important;border-radius: 14px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017904\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf505fd7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbO2eLCoP0mz9iag901uGUbnZM7J3ZkFoib2EqHNGO38f3MIywY8WqWHX2Dx2hdX8JvT6ibBApgsHH3AsN3ic4XaHYLAIIcyMGkGpY4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;font-weight: 700;margin: 32px 0px 14px;padding-left: 12px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(215, 26, 27);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;line-height: 1.35 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">开始倾销后，我们实际用得更多了</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两家大哥开始倾销以后，我的使用AI习惯变得更加奔放，尤其是有小龙虾的加持。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">就拿我Codex主账号来说，这周才过去两天，周限额就用完了，这还是在两倍限额的前提下……</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5738161559888579\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2872\" style=\"display: block;width: 100%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;box-shadow: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22) 0px 16px 34px, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12) 0px 4px 10px;border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);margin: 30px auto !important;padding: 8px !important;border-radius: 14px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017906\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=793e1ac9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbN9YyUXn1c9JXT0kLhvIFzm2coCvzibzzq4Vy9H8RFXA7m3lYRf1HSP6quztelwFMyAuYDQib5ZhErviburzwrueaBql8cjUYFgks%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code和Codex的$200/月的套餐，目前我都是分别两个账号了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">非常像去年国内外卖大战的时候，外卖便宜了，大家点的外卖更多了，花在外卖上的钱其实更多了。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;font-weight: 700;margin: 32px 0px 14px;padding-left: 12px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(215, 26, 27);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;line-height: 1.35 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“中转站”对于用户来说，已经不香了</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这样官方折扣力度下，中转站的用户，已经非常不香了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你想想看，你随便买个20美元每个月的套餐，不管是这两家的哪一家，其实你一个月真实消耗的token可以超过600美金， 相当于0.3折。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你买的是200美元每个月的套餐，那你每个月真实消耗的token价值可以轻松超过1万美金。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">稳定的、不掺假的中转站，往往是2~6折卖token给用户。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">也就是说，你作为用户，你显然是买官方的要更划算的多。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但如果你作为中转站的商家，0.2折的成本卖给人家5折，只要你能卖的出去并且保证稳定，这个生意模型还挺好的……</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;font-weight: 700;margin: 32px 0px 14px;padding-left: 12px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(215, 26, 27);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;line-height: 1.35 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的看法</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一，抓紧薅。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">聪明人在别人烧钱的时候建产品，而不是建依赖。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">抓紧跑通你的产品验证、积累你的用户，这些是补贴结束后也带得走的东西。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二，无论是“养虾”还是“养你自己”，都需要喂上好的饲料。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我知道买官方账号很难。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是最顶级的大模型都已经便宜成这样了，克服万难，也请你要用上官方的顶级模型包月套餐。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">（别再留言区问了，不会回复“怎么买”这样话题。）</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三，模型能力的差距在缩小，生态才是护城河。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugging Face 热榜上已经有人用 Claude Opus 4.6 的 API 蒸馏出了开源模型，几万个赞，它可以让Qwen开源的模型拥有超过Sonnet 4.5的写代码能力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">当\"我比你聪明\"这张牌越来越难打，竞争就变成了—— 谁的工具链最深入你的日常工作流。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是为什么 Anthropic 赌长上下文，OpenAI 赌 Codex。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它们要的不是你用一次，是你离不开。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后提醒一句</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">薅羊毛可以，薅的时候一定要清醒——谁是羊</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">期待你的反馈。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">💡最后放个小广告，3月19日，我的AI编程课正式开始！现在报名，下周见！&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247501473&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=69098ca647a0abd1a4a7cfc03f0b05f4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"刘小排终于发布AI编程课了\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">刘小排终于发布AI编程课了</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文分析了 Anthropic 与 OpenAI 近期通过翻倍用量和取消溢价开启的“价格战”，探讨了其对 RAG 架构、中转站市场及开发者工作流的深远影响。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文分析了 Anthropic 与 OpenAI 近期通过翻倍用量和取消溢价开启的“价格战”，探讨了其对 RAG 架构、中转站市场及开发者工作流的深远影响。",
  "summary": "文章指出 AI 领域正上演类似“外卖大战”的倾销竞争。Anthropic 通过 Claude Code 提供 100 万 token 且不加收溢价，并针对非高峰时段（对中国用户极为有利）提供双倍额度；OpenAI 则通过 Codex 限额翻倍显著提升了活跃用户数。作者认为，这种官方大规模补贴使得第三方“中转站”失去价格优势。竞争核心已从模型智力转向工具链对工作流的渗透。作者建议开发者应利用补贴红利期，使用官方顶级模型快速验证产品，而非仅仅建立对补贴的依赖。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 巨头开启“倾销”模式，旨在通过高额补贴深度渗透用户工作流。",
      "explanation": "Anthropic 取消长上下文溢价并提供闲时双倍额度，OpenAI 翻倍 Codex 限额，均显示出竞争重心已转向用户留存与生态占领。"
    },
    {
      "point": "超长上下文的普及可能对传统 RAG 框架造成“灭顶之灾”。",
      "explanation": "随着 1M 以上上下文窗口成本降低且不再加价，Agent 可以直接处理海量信息，减少了对复杂检索增强生成架构的依赖。"
    },
    {
      "point": "官方订阅的极高性价比正在瓦解第三方 API 中转站的市场空间。",
      "explanation": "在官方补贴下，20-200 美元的套餐可消耗价值数千甚至上万美金的 token，使得中转站的转售模式在稳定性和价格上均失去竞争力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "中国开发者在这一轮 AI 价格战中享有独特的“时区红利”。",
      "explanation": "美东时间的非高峰时段恰好覆盖了北京时间的大部分工作时间，使得国内用户能天然享受双倍额度而无需刻意调整作息。"
    }
  ],
